author: FROM STAFF REPORTS
title: Virginia's Collins wins Riviera/ITA All-American tennis crown
text:
Virginia's Collins wins Riviera/ITA All-American tennis crown FROM STAFF REPORTS The Daily Progress 
PACIFIC PALISADES, Calif. â€” Senior Danielle Collins posted her second championship in a prestigious national tournament Sunday, cruising in straight sets to claim the Riviera/ITA All-American Championship. 
Collins defeated Sinead Lohan of Miami, 6-1, 6-2, to grab the championship of the event. Just a month earlier, Collins claimed the championship at the Oracle/ITA Masters tournament in California.
